{"tid":921361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界大戰]俄羅斯要開打了？大批坦克緊急開赴邊境","createTime":"2018-11-29T13:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T14:47:12.000Z","uid":184581,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"16616ea348e9c2af83e17f539eea30b2d46bbdef","tid":921361,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭軍艦強闖刻赤海峽，俄軍猛烈開火，打傷並逮捕多名烏軍船員，烏軍艦艇也被悉數扣留，烏克蘭宣布&ldquo;全軍備戰&rdquo;，普京下令坦克向邊境集結，一場大戰能否避免？<br />\n<br />\n據海外網11月28日援引新加坡&ldquo;聯合早報&rdquo;的報導，烏克蘭總統波羅申科就近期俄烏關係發表講話時指出，俄羅斯正在向俄烏邊境增兵，雙方隨時可能&ldquo;爆發全面戰爭&rdquo;。波羅申科表示，在俄烏邊境的俄軍坦克比平時整整&ldquo;多了三倍&rdquo;，位於邊境的機械化步兵數量也&ldquo;急劇增加&rdquo;，烏克蘭面臨與俄羅斯&ldquo;全面開戰&rdquo;的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，引發俄烏新一輪戰爭威脅的是最近烏克蘭的一次挑釁行動。11月25日，烏克蘭海軍2艘砲艇和1艘拖船，在企圖強行穿越刻赤海峽時被俄軍攔截，在此過程中雙方發生了短暫而激烈的交火，6名烏克蘭船員受傷。俄羅斯指控烏克蘭海軍企圖擅闖俄方領海，而烏克蘭則重申對亞速海的主權，聲稱有權通過刻赤海峽，而無需接受俄羅斯的管理。目前烏克蘭3艘艦艇及其人員已經被俄羅斯扣留，事件影響依然在持續發酵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d0ac1f0044e7d5901d689110bd6939beb6f08c","tid":921361,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"ww3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n渣住廚師腸就有女屌！"},{"pid":"8ee8bfa76906b67c0bdae70eca80cb350bcaca79","tid":921361,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"我要成為烏克蘭妹難民之父"},{"pid":"92b2686caed9d31e95f61113c5988b9924ed84a6","tid":921361,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔打正契弟"},{"pid":"a1d2e874af34533e3c17f2cdd709876a5faaea55","tid":921361,"uid":20836,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"世界大戰抹黑宇宙了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cde4fb4668d01a63f1625a9814cdbcbafe96da9","tid":921361,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"WW3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b083b913303829cac3ad8851434c24bacb7f2dd","tid":921361,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"如果真係開打ww3仲駛唔駛開工？"},{"pid":"a87f33e0c067a8e186bf95bfc77d2a82dbd38a16","tid":921361,"uid":190066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"001b2a3ea3d738341a58ef195c08b87165902a20","tid":921361,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b083b913303829cac3ad8851434c24bacb7f2dd","tid":921361,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"如果真係開打ww3仲駛唔駛開工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"有冇砲彈打中你公司？<br />\n就算打中咗，有冇打中埋 back up office ?"},{"pid":"7d7bc8bbddce2d58654c5ac17b57b36107b167ca","tid":921361,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001b2a3ea3d738341a58ef195c08b87165902a20","tid":921361,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b083b913303829cac3ad8851434c24bacb7f2dd","tid":921361,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"如果真係開打ww3仲駛唔駛開工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"有冇砲彈打中你公司？<br />\n就算打中咗，有冇打中埋 back up office ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:06:30.000Z","msg":"home office囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2556481ecbb57f682a503b40d04ccd5d1dff92fa","tid":921361,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7bc8bbddce2d58654c5ac17b57b36107b167ca","tid":921361,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001b2a3ea3d738341a58ef195c08b87165902a20","tid":921361,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p